1
00:00:11,640 --> 00:00:18,320
[2012]

2
00:00:11,800 --> 00:00:12,430
Qi Yan.

3
00:00:15,430 --> 00:00:17,760
You've caused serious trouble this time.

4
00:00:18,390 --> 00:00:19,030
Really?

5
00:00:19,710 --> 00:00:21,070
You killed a cop!

6
00:00:22,350 --> 00:00:25,210
Dad's factory
in the mountains was also taken down.

7
00:00:25,640 --> 00:00:26,600
He is furious.

8
00:00:27,710 --> 00:00:28,960
Now Dad suspects

9
00:00:30,990 --> 00:00:33,190
that the factory's location was leaked

10
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:37,020
because you couldn't keep your mouth shut.

11
00:00:37,490 --> 00:00:38,130
What?

12
00:00:40,620 --> 00:00:42,750
Does Wen Hongsheng want to silence me?

13
00:00:43,030 --> 00:00:44,310
Why would you think that?

14
00:00:44,310 --> 00:00:45,880
How could I not think that?

15
00:00:48,670 --> 00:00:50,240
He's always disliked me.

16
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:52,470
Ever since you brought me back

17
00:00:52,470 --> 00:00:54,030
to your so-called home,

18
00:00:55,710 --> 00:00:57,240
he's wanted to get rid of me.

19
00:00:59,630 --> 00:01:00,270
Qi Yan,

20
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,530
I'm only going to ask you one question.

21
00:01:06,160 --> 00:01:07,160
Does it really...

22
00:01:09,190 --> 00:01:10,720
have nothing to do with you?

23
00:01:13,380 --> 00:01:14,610
You don't believe me?

24
00:01:18,030 --> 00:01:19,890
Even you don't believe me, do you?

25
00:01:27,580 --> 00:01:28,730
No one believes me.

26
00:01:30,500 --> 00:01:32,890
I only wanted to chat with Ming!

27
00:01:33,340 --> 00:01:35,780
How was I supposed to know
the cops would show up?

28
00:01:35,780 --> 00:01:37,509
Did I want to get caught by them?

29
00:01:37,810 --> 00:01:39,580
Did I want to die?

30
00:01:43,580 --> 00:01:44,220
It's fine.

31
00:01:45,360 --> 00:01:47,340
Ming will take the fall for everything.

32
00:01:47,340 --> 00:01:48,070
Don't worry.

33
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:50,740
I can never be in the light.

34
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:55,450
I can never live in broad daylight.

35
00:01:58,720 --> 00:02:00,250
I want to be like you,

36
00:02:01,830 --> 00:02:03,090
standing in the light.

37
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:08,280
I'm scared.

38
00:02:10,090 --> 00:02:11,810
I'm really scared.

39
00:02:32,690 --> 00:02:33,340
I'm sorry,

40
00:02:34,850 --> 00:02:35,500
Qi Yan.

41
00:02:38,300 --> 00:02:39,940
Maybe this is just my fate.

42
00:02:41,300 --> 00:02:43,570
The cops have blocked every way out now.

43
00:02:44,780 --> 00:02:45,900
I need a place

44
00:02:47,340 --> 00:02:48,060
to hide.

45
00:02:49,220 --> 00:02:50,880
Just like when we were kids...

46
00:02:56,220 --> 00:02:57,780
in Mom's closet.

47
00:03:24,220 --> 00:03:25,500
I know a place.

48
00:03:29,060 --> 00:03:30,500
Dad has a warehouse here.

49
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:33,300
You can hide in there for a while.

50
00:03:33,740 --> 00:03:34,600
It's very safe.

51
00:03:35,250 --> 00:03:35,970
Very safe.

52
00:05:05,690 --> 00:05:11,430
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

53
00:05:11,790 --> 00:05:14,090
[Episode 26]

54
00:06:26,500 --> 00:06:27,420
Officer Zhou,

55
00:06:29,210 --> 00:06:30,210
nice to meet you.

56
00:06:31,940 --> 00:06:34,690
And it's an honor to have you
listen to me play the piano.

57
00:06:34,690 --> 00:06:35,550
How do you feel?

58
00:06:37,100 --> 00:06:39,100
I once planned to kill you right away

59
00:06:39,659 --> 00:06:41,010
and gouge out your eyes

60
00:06:41,100 --> 00:06:42,560
to give to Jiang Hansheng.

61
00:06:44,010 --> 00:06:46,670
But you look really beautiful
in this red dress.

62
00:06:48,740 --> 00:06:49,810
So gorgeous.

63
00:06:51,500 --> 00:06:52,210
So,

64
00:06:53,810 --> 00:06:54,810
I changed my mind.

65
00:06:57,570 --> 00:06:58,659
A beautiful woman

66
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:02,830
should die a beautiful death.

67
00:07:04,330 --> 00:07:05,330
I personally don't like

68
00:07:05,330 --> 00:07:06,660
inartistic behaviors.

69
00:07:07,450 --> 00:07:08,450
So, Officer Zhou,

70
00:07:09,450 --> 00:07:11,380
I'd like to apologize to you first.

71
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:13,450
Were it not for Jiang Hansheng,

72
00:07:13,450 --> 00:07:14,980
our meeting would have been

73
00:07:19,140 --> 00:07:20,430
much more elegant.

74
00:07:24,870 --> 00:07:26,600
You are just like your husband.

75
00:07:27,690 --> 00:07:29,220
When I express my goodwill,

76
00:07:30,190 --> 00:07:31,240
you both like...

77
00:07:33,850 --> 00:07:35,310
You like to remain silent.

78
00:07:40,850 --> 00:07:42,159
Do you feel them?

79
00:07:43,250 --> 00:07:46,170
Do you feel
the cartilage and muscles here?

80
00:07:47,830 --> 00:07:49,190
They are very fragile,

81
00:07:50,409 --> 00:07:51,140
aren't they?

82
00:07:52,770 --> 00:07:53,980
So, Officer Zhou,

83
00:07:55,450 --> 00:07:56,890
say something.

84
00:07:58,520 --> 00:08:00,320
It's good for you.

85
00:08:05,010 --> 00:08:08,010
Did you do the same thing
to Zhao Xiaoyu and the others?

86
00:08:16,570 --> 00:08:18,500
So this is the first thing you said.

87
00:08:20,610 --> 00:08:21,740
How disappointing.

88
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:26,610
They were all failed works.

89
00:08:28,620 --> 00:08:30,890
So they were not qualified to come here.

90
00:08:32,610 --> 00:08:34,270
There isn't anything special

91
00:08:34,340 --> 00:08:35,740
about your concert hall.

92
00:08:37,970 --> 00:08:38,610
Is that so?

93
00:08:48,780 --> 00:08:50,980
Do you know who this place was set up for?

94
00:08:53,490 --> 00:08:54,490
My elder brother.

95
00:08:56,420 --> 00:08:57,850
The one who chose
to surrender 5 years ago,

96
00:08:57,850 --> 00:08:59,140
but was still shot

97
00:08:59,140 --> 00:09:00,810
and killed by your husband.

98
00:09:01,490 --> 00:09:03,490
My twin brother.

99
00:09:08,610 --> 00:09:09,690
So, Officer Zhou,

100
00:09:10,780 --> 00:09:12,570
do you know why

101
00:09:12,570 --> 00:09:14,610
I brought you here now?

102
00:09:27,870 --> 00:09:28,460
Chief Tan.

103
00:09:28,460 --> 00:09:29,060
Bai Yang,

104
00:09:29,090 --> 00:09:30,180
I've applied for this case

105
00:09:30,180 --> 00:09:31,860
and the attack on Director Wang Pengze

106
00:09:31,860 --> 00:09:34,020
to be merged
into the 8/17 Case's task force.

107
00:09:34,020 --> 00:09:35,440
We will participate directly
in the investigation.

108
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:37,390
The documents for the joint task force
will be issued soon.

109
00:09:37,390 --> 00:09:38,570
You should proceed accordingly.

110
00:09:38,570 --> 00:09:39,540
Okay, understood.

111
00:09:39,540 --> 00:09:41,200
How is Professor Jiang doing?

112
00:09:43,980 --> 00:09:45,950
Can't tell right now.

113
00:09:45,970 --> 00:09:47,430
But he's still quite calm.

114
00:09:48,020 --> 00:09:49,470
Okay, got it.

115
00:09:52,730 --> 00:09:53,490
Chief Tan,

116
00:09:53,530 --> 00:09:55,390
Zhou Jin's car accident report is out.

117
00:09:55,390 --> 00:09:56,490
I'll send you a copy.

118
00:09:56,490 --> 00:09:57,020
Okay.

119
00:10:03,090 --> 00:10:04,070
Wait, Officer Jiang.

120
00:10:04,070 --> 00:10:05,210
You haven't been reinstated yet.

121
00:10:05,210 --> 00:10:05,660
You can't participate.

122
00:10:05,660 --> 00:10:07,060
Where is Jiang Hansheng?

123
00:10:09,020 --> 00:10:09,590
Well...

124
00:10:09,670 --> 00:10:10,420
Officer Jiang.

125
00:10:10,420 --> 00:10:11,680
Officer Jiang, you...

126
00:10:12,900 --> 00:10:15,050
As an insider, I have the right
to assist in the investigation.

127
00:10:15,050 --> 00:10:16,170
It's dated today.

128
00:10:34,870 --> 00:10:36,470
You have one chance to speak.

129
00:10:37,730 --> 00:10:38,730
Professor Jiang!

130
00:10:39,220 --> 00:10:40,080
Officer Jiang.

131
00:10:40,470 --> 00:10:41,190
Zhou Jin's

132
00:10:41,470 --> 00:10:43,670
accident investigation report is out.

133
00:10:44,730 --> 00:10:45,330
Go ahead.

134
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:47,660
Chief Zhan from the Information Department

135
00:10:47,660 --> 00:10:49,380
of the Provincial Bureau is awake
at the hospital.

136
00:10:49,380 --> 00:10:50,110
Zhan Wei?

137
00:10:50,740 --> 00:10:51,330
Yes.

138
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:54,240
He said his child
just had a one-month party.

139
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,840
Zhou Jin told him
that she was in Jingzhou on business

140
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:57,260
and wanted to visit the child by the way.

141
00:10:57,260 --> 00:10:59,260
So he drove to pick Zhou Jin up today.

142
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:01,060
On the way, he suddenly found
that the brakes failed.

143
00:11:01,060 --> 00:11:01,960
After losing control of the steering,

144
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:03,350
he crashed
right into the roadside barrier.

145
00:11:03,350 --> 00:11:05,180
He jumped out of the car
in advance to survive.

146
00:11:05,180 --> 00:11:06,020
Because he fell hard,

147
00:11:06,020 --> 00:11:07,420
he passed out after that.

148
00:11:07,610 --> 00:11:08,610
But he is very sure

149
00:11:08,780 --> 00:11:09,570
that before he fainted,

150
00:11:09,570 --> 00:11:10,940
he saw a black sedan

151
00:11:10,940 --> 00:11:11,970
take Zhou Jin away.

152
00:11:11,970 --> 00:11:13,870
The Provincial Bureau
has verified the statement.

153
00:11:13,870 --> 00:11:15,570
It basically matches the scene.

154
00:11:15,570 --> 00:11:16,970
The traffic accident department said

155
00:11:16,970 --> 00:11:18,730
the brake line was tampered with.

156
00:11:18,730 --> 00:11:19,850
But as for who did it,

157
00:11:19,850 --> 00:11:21,140
Zhan Wei has no clue, either.

158
00:11:21,140 --> 00:11:22,450
We've got someone on guard
at the hospital now.

159
00:11:22,450 --> 00:11:24,200
Just keep an eye on him normally.

160
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:26,060
You think Zhan Wei is suspicious?

161
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:31,420
Where are you going?

162
00:11:31,420 --> 00:11:32,350
To the hospital.

163
00:11:41,730 --> 00:11:42,460
This clock is

164
00:11:43,070 --> 00:11:44,070
going backwards.

165
00:11:46,790 --> 00:11:48,330
He only gave us 4 hours.

166
00:11:54,990 --> 00:11:55,990
Professor Jiang.

167
00:11:56,680 --> 00:11:57,290
Wan,

168
00:11:57,450 --> 00:11:58,350
it's in Room 2110.

169
00:11:58,350 --> 00:11:59,090
We're going to find someone.

170
00:11:59,090 --> 00:11:59,490
Okay.

171
00:11:59,510 --> 00:12:00,040
Go ahead.

172
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:14,800
Do you need me to do anything?

173
00:12:25,560 --> 00:12:26,710
You stay in the car.

174
00:12:44,780 --> 00:12:46,710
How much do you know about Zhan Wei?

175
00:12:46,750 --> 00:12:48,810
How confident are you in your judgment?

176
00:12:48,810 --> 00:12:49,780
We don't have time right now

177
00:12:49,780 --> 00:12:52,510
to verify that the judgment is
completely right.

178
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:58,120
I thought

179
00:12:58,150 --> 00:12:59,700
you were the gentle type.

180
00:13:02,970 --> 00:13:04,170
I hope you can help me.

181
00:13:05,610 --> 00:13:06,740
I'm not helping you.

182
00:13:13,330 --> 00:13:13,900
Alright,

183
00:13:14,210 --> 00:13:15,050
the wound's been treated.

184
00:13:15,050 --> 00:13:16,310
Stay here a bit longer.

185
00:13:36,790 --> 00:13:37,790
Professor Jiang,

186
00:13:38,380 --> 00:13:39,440
what are you doing?

187
00:13:39,940 --> 00:13:40,940
Where is Zhou Jin?

188
00:13:41,900 --> 00:13:43,500
How would I know where she is?

189
00:13:43,660 --> 00:13:44,850
I'm so sorry

190
00:13:45,620 --> 00:13:46,760
about what happened to Jin.

191
00:13:46,760 --> 00:13:47,780
But I really didn't know

192
00:13:47,780 --> 00:13:49,020
they would kidnap her.

193
00:13:49,020 --> 00:13:50,420
They tampered with my brakes.

194
00:13:50,420 --> 00:13:51,490
I almost died, too!

195
00:13:52,680 --> 00:13:54,610
You know I have no direct evidence,

196
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:57,330
so you want to deny it to the end, right?

197
00:13:57,330 --> 00:13:58,780
I also see Jin as my younger sister.

198
00:13:58,780 --> 00:14:00,210
How could I possibly harm her?

199
00:14:00,210 --> 00:14:02,740
Your career's taken off
over the past 5 years.

200
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:04,680
Zhou Chuan up there in heaven

201
00:14:05,250 --> 00:14:07,180
would also feel happy for you, huh?

202
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:13,330
You think I'm here to scare you?

203
00:14:14,090 --> 00:14:15,700
You don't have much time left.

204
00:14:15,700 --> 00:14:17,230
Don't waste your time on me.

205
00:14:17,260 --> 00:14:19,720
I'm not here to talk
about evidence with you.

206
00:14:20,730 --> 00:14:22,930
I heard you value your family very much.

207
00:14:24,580 --> 00:14:25,510
What do you mean?

208
00:14:32,340 --> 00:14:34,250
Please, don't hurt my child!

209
00:14:34,510 --> 00:14:35,970
My child is still so little!

210
00:14:35,970 --> 00:14:36,780
Chief Zhan!

211
00:14:36,860 --> 00:14:38,540
Come back quickly, Chief Zhan!

212
00:14:38,540 --> 00:14:39,940
What are you trying to do?

213
00:14:40,140 --> 00:14:41,070
Jiang Hansheng,

214
00:14:41,210 --> 00:14:42,470
you're threatening me?

215
00:14:42,470 --> 00:14:43,860
Do you really dare to make a move?

216
00:14:43,860 --> 00:14:44,790
Look carefully.

217
00:14:45,230 --> 00:14:46,250
I'm not the one doing it.

218
00:14:46,250 --> 00:14:47,920
You are an accomplice, equally guilty!

219
00:14:47,920 --> 00:14:49,040
I just told him

220
00:14:49,550 --> 00:14:51,880
that it was you
who betrayed the police back then.

221
00:14:51,880 --> 00:14:54,180
It was you who leaked the information
about the undercover officers

222
00:14:54,180 --> 00:14:55,900
engaged in the 8/17 Case task force.

223
00:14:55,900 --> 00:14:56,380
I didn't!

224
00:14:56,380 --> 00:14:56,850
I never did that!

225
00:14:56,850 --> 00:14:58,250
Whether you did it or not,

226
00:14:59,040 --> 00:15:00,170
would he believe it?

227
00:15:00,630 --> 00:15:01,180
He?

228
00:15:02,140 --> 00:15:02,900
Who is he?

229
00:15:03,490 --> 00:15:04,820
What right does he have?

230
00:15:10,800 --> 00:15:11,900
I am Jiang Cheng.

231
00:15:12,020 --> 00:15:14,180
Do you think I have the right?

232
00:15:15,220 --> 00:15:15,750
Jiang...

233
00:15:16,170 --> 00:15:16,900
Jiang Cheng.

234
00:15:18,060 --> 00:15:18,640
Jiang Cheng,

235
00:15:18,640 --> 00:15:19,380
listen to me.

236
00:15:20,610 --> 00:15:21,810
I really didn't do it.

237
00:15:22,020 --> 00:15:22,680
I really...

238
00:15:22,930 --> 00:15:24,790
We used to be good buddies, right?

239
00:15:24,940 --> 00:15:27,560
I can't believe you actually
stabbed me in the back.

240
00:15:27,560 --> 00:15:28,710
Not to mention that Yao Weihai

241
00:15:28,710 --> 00:15:30,760
and Meng Junfeng died such tragic deaths.

242
00:15:30,760 --> 00:15:32,330
Do you think I'll let go of the one

243
00:15:32,330 --> 00:15:34,460
who betrayed them behind their backs?

244
00:15:35,210 --> 00:15:35,740
Cheng...

245
00:15:36,060 --> 00:15:36,610
Cheng...

246
00:15:37,260 --> 00:15:38,060
Believe me,

247
00:15:38,060 --> 00:15:39,540
I... I really didn't do it.

248
00:15:39,610 --> 00:15:40,270
Believe me.

249
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:50,960
My chips are pretty clear now.

250
00:15:51,870 --> 00:15:52,620
Your turn.

251
00:15:54,300 --> 00:15:54,660
I...

252
00:15:55,460 --> 00:15:57,460
don't know.

253
00:16:01,410 --> 00:16:02,490
Nanshan Manor.

254
00:16:03,090 --> 00:16:04,570
I only know the name of the place.

255
00:16:04,570 --> 00:16:05,950
It's called Nanshan Manor.

256
00:16:05,950 --> 00:16:07,270
Old Scorpion told me that.

257
00:16:07,270 --> 00:16:09,130
He asked me to meet Zhou Jin alone.

258
00:16:10,450 --> 00:16:11,780
Where is Nanshan Manor?

259
00:16:13,490 --> 00:16:14,220
I don't know.

260
00:16:14,900 --> 00:16:15,700
I've checked.

261
00:16:16,490 --> 00:16:18,420
There's no such place in Jingzhou.

262
00:16:22,260 --> 00:16:23,060
Zhan Wei!

263
00:16:25,210 --> 00:16:25,900
Zhan Wei!

264
00:16:25,900 --> 00:16:26,830
What's going on?

265
00:16:27,140 --> 00:16:28,140
Professor Jiang!

266
00:16:28,490 --> 00:16:29,970
You put the pocket watch

267
00:16:31,420 --> 00:16:32,590
by Zhou Chuan's tomb, didn't you?

268
00:16:32,590 --> 00:16:33,650
I'll go get the key!

269
00:16:34,380 --> 00:16:35,020
Excuse me, excuse me.

270
00:16:35,020 --> 00:16:35,570
Zhan Wei!

271
00:16:37,720 --> 00:16:38,430
Hurry!

272
00:16:38,450 --> 00:16:38,930
Coming!

273
00:16:41,730 --> 00:16:42,730
Professor Jiang!

274
00:16:43,460 --> 00:16:44,460
Professor Jiang!

275
00:16:44,610 --> 00:16:45,610
Professor Jiang,

276
00:16:45,730 --> 00:16:46,440
calm down.

277
00:16:46,470 --> 00:16:48,000
Calm down. Don't go too far.

278
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:48,870
Who are you?

279
00:16:48,970 --> 00:16:50,430
What were you trying to do?

280
00:16:50,630 --> 00:16:51,960
I'm Zhou Jin's husband.

281
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:53,280
Professor Jiang!

282
00:16:53,490 --> 00:16:54,570
What's going on?

283
00:16:58,610 --> 00:16:59,540
What happened?

284
00:17:00,970 --> 00:17:03,780
There was a misunderstanding
between Professor Jiang and me,

285
00:17:03,780 --> 00:17:05,420
but it's over now.

286
00:17:14,490 --> 00:17:15,220
Got nothing?

287
00:17:16,530 --> 00:17:17,250
Not sure yet.

288
00:17:17,250 --> 00:17:18,310
What have you done?

289
00:17:18,940 --> 00:17:19,420
Well,

290
00:17:20,010 --> 00:17:21,849
the task force
has already sent police to search.

291
00:17:21,849 --> 00:17:24,010
The tech department is also
checking the surveillance along the way.

292
00:17:24,010 --> 00:17:25,940
Maybe they'll have some good news.

293
00:17:25,980 --> 00:17:27,640
Did you find Zhou Jin's phone?

294
00:17:27,690 --> 00:17:29,120
We found it at the crash scene,

295
00:17:29,120 --> 00:17:30,380
but it's been smashed to pieces.

296
00:17:30,380 --> 00:17:32,710
It will take some time
to recover the data.

297
00:17:41,160 --> 00:17:42,050
No!

298
00:17:43,800 --> 00:17:45,150
Lu Xin!

299
00:18:04,630 --> 00:18:06,030
Is that Professor Jiang?

300
00:18:06,720 --> 00:18:07,760
I-It's me.

301
00:18:08,900 --> 00:18:10,010
I am Qi Zhen.

302
00:18:12,890 --> 00:18:14,890
I have already arrived in Jingzhou.

303
00:18:18,800 --> 00:18:19,710
Last time,

304
00:18:20,190 --> 00:18:22,250
you and Officer Zhou came to my house.

305
00:18:22,770 --> 00:18:24,660
Sorry, because

306
00:18:25,120 --> 00:18:27,140
I was not
in a good state of mind back then,

307
00:18:27,140 --> 00:18:28,250
I kicked you out.

308
00:18:29,290 --> 00:18:30,420
It was because

309
00:18:31,050 --> 00:18:32,340
I was terrified.

310
00:18:33,450 --> 00:18:34,010
I...

311
00:18:34,730 --> 00:18:35,970
I was very scared...

312
00:18:37,990 --> 00:18:39,800
that Wen Hongsheng would come to hurt me

313
00:18:39,800 --> 00:18:41,110
and hurt Jian Liang.

314
00:18:42,380 --> 00:18:43,010
So,

315
00:18:43,600 --> 00:18:44,320
I'm sorry.

316
00:18:46,800 --> 00:18:48,120
Jian Liang told me.

317
00:18:48,450 --> 00:18:49,140
He said

318
00:18:49,730 --> 00:18:51,530
if you cannot face your past,

319
00:18:52,360 --> 00:18:53,520
there is no way

320
00:18:54,370 --> 00:18:56,020
for you to start a new life.

321
00:18:58,730 --> 00:19:01,140
I am willing to tell you
everything I know.

322
00:19:02,290 --> 00:19:04,150
Who did you say you were afraid of?

323
00:19:04,590 --> 00:19:05,450
Wen Hongsheng?

324
00:19:06,140 --> 00:19:07,540
How do you spell the name?

325
00:19:09,020 --> 00:19:11,060
"W-e-n" as in news,

326
00:19:12,050 --> 00:19:13,420
"H-o-n-g" as in wild goose,

327
00:19:13,420 --> 00:19:15,020
and "s-h-e-n-g" as in grand.

328
00:19:15,210 --> 00:19:17,070
Wen Hongsheng is Qi Yan's father?

329
00:19:19,060 --> 00:19:19,610
Yes.

330
00:19:20,940 --> 00:19:21,620
He is.

331
00:19:23,420 --> 00:19:24,970
I was 17

332
00:19:24,970 --> 00:19:26,580
when I met Wen Hongsheng.

333
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:27,770
At that time,

334
00:19:28,140 --> 00:19:29,380
I hadn't finished high school

335
00:19:29,380 --> 00:19:30,510
and had dropped out.

336
00:19:30,900 --> 00:19:33,160
I worked in a towel factory
during the day

337
00:19:33,330 --> 00:19:33,960
and had

338
00:19:34,530 --> 00:19:37,290
a part-time job
selling soda in a pool hall at night

339
00:19:37,290 --> 00:19:38,350
to make more money.

340
00:19:40,620 --> 00:19:41,620
Give me 2 sodas!

341
00:19:41,900 --> 00:19:42,490
Coming.

342
00:19:47,660 --> 00:19:48,790
Here are your sodas.

343
00:19:52,940 --> 00:19:54,180
I can hardly remember

344
00:19:54,180 --> 00:19:56,290
what happened during that time now.

345
00:19:56,620 --> 00:19:59,250
I just remember
that after I got with Wen Hongsheng,

346
00:19:59,250 --> 00:20:00,580
he treated me very badly

347
00:20:01,290 --> 00:20:02,580
and often hit me.

348
00:20:03,620 --> 00:20:05,750
He wasn't doing legitimate business.

349
00:20:06,920 --> 00:20:07,730
He only did

350
00:20:08,060 --> 00:20:09,820
shady business.

351
00:20:10,380 --> 00:20:12,000
On the surface, he was in foreign trade,

352
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:13,300
selling medicinal herbs,

353
00:20:13,300 --> 00:20:14,100
but secretly,

354
00:20:14,370 --> 00:20:16,230
he did whatever made quick money.

355
00:20:17,940 --> 00:20:19,000
I wanted to escape,

356
00:20:20,250 --> 00:20:21,820
but every time I ran away,

357
00:20:22,350 --> 00:20:24,630
I only ended up being beaten severely.

358
00:20:24,660 --> 00:20:25,700
How dare you run!

359
00:20:27,420 --> 00:20:28,450
How dare you run!

360
00:20:32,370 --> 00:20:33,250
Later,

361
00:20:34,860 --> 00:20:36,390
I learned to behave myself.

362
00:20:37,940 --> 00:20:40,870
There was even a time
when I started to accept my fate.

363
00:20:41,100 --> 00:20:41,620
Until

364
00:20:42,860 --> 00:20:43,860
I got pregnant.

365
00:20:46,450 --> 00:20:47,820
At that time, Wen Hongsheng was

366
00:20:47,820 --> 00:20:49,080
carried away with joy.

367
00:20:50,420 --> 00:20:53,220
He told me that as long as I gave birth
to a son of his,

368
00:20:53,530 --> 00:20:54,290
he would renovate

369
00:20:54,290 --> 00:20:56,890
the large villa in the suburbs
and give it to me.

370
00:20:57,210 --> 00:20:59,810
And he'd pass
all the family business to my son.

371
00:21:00,380 --> 00:21:02,180
He thought it was a reward for me,

372
00:21:02,710 --> 00:21:03,970
a favor bestowed on me.

373
00:21:04,660 --> 00:21:05,720
But when I heard it,

374
00:21:06,940 --> 00:21:08,340
it chilled me to the bone.

375
00:21:10,420 --> 00:21:11,950
They were also my children.

376
00:21:12,520 --> 00:21:14,010
I'd never bear to see my child

377
00:21:14,010 --> 00:21:15,530
become someone like him.

378
00:22:01,490 --> 00:22:03,090
Where exactly is this place?

379
00:22:04,770 --> 00:22:05,380
Home.

380
00:22:06,010 --> 00:22:06,530
Home?

381
00:22:11,250 --> 00:22:13,250
It's only a home if there are people.

382
00:22:13,730 --> 00:22:15,020
Besides you, is there

383
00:22:16,100 --> 00:22:17,100
anyone else here?

384
00:22:19,310 --> 00:22:20,170
Anyone else...

385
00:22:23,040 --> 00:22:24,630
Other people...

386
00:22:33,900 --> 00:22:34,580
Home...

387
00:22:37,250 --> 00:22:39,860
It is indeed a very distant concept.

388
00:22:43,450 --> 00:22:44,910
It was after I got pregnant

389
00:22:45,270 --> 00:22:48,730
that Wen Hongsheng gradually stopped
watching me so closely.

390
00:22:49,140 --> 00:22:50,210
I took advantage of a chance

391
00:22:50,210 --> 00:22:51,620
to go out shopping

392
00:22:52,290 --> 00:22:54,090
and sneaked back to my hometown.

393
00:22:54,820 --> 00:22:56,250
With my cousin's help,

394
00:22:56,270 --> 00:22:56,940
I went

395
00:22:56,940 --> 00:22:58,870
to a small town where no one knew me.

396
00:22:59,660 --> 00:23:00,790
I started a new life.

397
00:23:02,430 --> 00:23:04,030
I worked in a garment factory

398
00:23:04,600 --> 00:23:05,730
and learned sewing.

399
00:23:06,380 --> 00:23:08,510
Then I gave birth to my children there.

400
00:23:09,740 --> 00:23:11,470
The elder one was named Qi Lang.

401
00:23:11,730 --> 00:23:13,530
The younger one was named Qi Yan.

402
00:23:13,890 --> 00:23:16,090
We lived peaceful lives for a few years.

403
00:23:16,860 --> 00:23:18,060
At the time, I thought

404
00:23:18,530 --> 00:23:21,040
that Wen Hongsheng was
no longer interested in me

405
00:23:21,040 --> 00:23:22,900
and wouldn't look for me anymore.

406
00:23:24,900 --> 00:23:25,970
But unexpectedly,

407
00:23:27,210 --> 00:23:29,210
he had been looking for me all along.

408
00:23:29,690 --> 00:23:30,620
When his underlings

409
00:23:30,620 --> 00:23:32,420
found the factory where I lived.

410
00:23:33,050 --> 00:23:36,180
Wen Hongsheng sent men
to catch me that day immediately.

411
00:23:36,420 --> 00:23:38,880
He became even more terrifying
than before.

412
00:23:39,760 --> 00:23:40,600
They had guns.

413
00:23:42,040 --> 00:23:44,040
His men all called him Old Scorpion.

414
00:23:46,320 --> 00:23:47,360
I could tell

415
00:23:49,300 --> 00:23:51,430
that there was nothing he dared not do.

416
00:23:58,120 --> 00:23:59,650
You've lost so much weight.

417
00:24:05,820 --> 00:24:06,820
I beg you.

418
00:24:08,690 --> 00:24:10,220
I don't want anything else.

419
00:24:10,420 --> 00:24:11,730
Please let me go.

420
00:24:13,380 --> 00:24:14,100
Zhen.

421
00:24:16,530 --> 00:24:18,790
You need to return what you stole from me.

422
00:24:20,020 --> 00:24:21,170
Where is my child?

423
00:24:25,180 --> 00:24:26,000
I aborted it.

424
00:24:31,950 --> 00:24:33,190
Where is

425
00:24:34,010 --> 00:24:35,100
my child?

426
00:24:36,360 --> 00:24:37,680
Didn't you get it?

427
00:24:39,190 --> 00:24:40,450
Right after I left you,

428
00:24:40,490 --> 00:24:41,880
I just aborted it!

429
00:24:42,840 --> 00:24:43,760
Wen Hongsheng,

430
00:24:44,500 --> 00:24:47,290
did you really think
I'd give birth to a child for you?

431
00:24:47,290 --> 00:24:49,140
Just hearing your breathing

432
00:24:49,490 --> 00:24:50,940
makes me sick!

433
00:24:55,380 --> 00:24:56,920
Go find my child.

434
00:25:03,050 --> 00:25:04,180
That was when I was 9.

435
00:25:07,050 --> 00:25:08,200
How I wish

436
00:25:12,010 --> 00:25:14,340
the one rushing out of that wardrobe was

437
00:25:17,900 --> 00:25:18,580
me,

438
00:25:21,820 --> 00:25:22,780
Qi Yan.

439
00:25:26,900 --> 00:25:28,160
Take good care of Mom.

440
00:25:28,190 --> 00:25:29,640
Wait for me to pick you up.

441
00:25:35,050 --> 00:25:36,380
Who told you to come out?

442
00:25:37,310 --> 00:25:40,040
When Wen Hongsheng was
about to start searching,

443
00:25:40,420 --> 00:25:41,340
Lang

444
00:25:43,100 --> 00:25:44,580
ran out by himself

445
00:25:45,100 --> 00:25:47,760
and said he was willing to go
with Wen Hongsheng.

446
00:25:49,140 --> 00:25:51,800
Wen Hongsheng didn't know
I gave birth to twins,

447
00:25:52,900 --> 00:25:54,360
so he didn't look for more.

448
00:25:55,290 --> 00:25:56,290
Take my son home.

449
00:25:57,860 --> 00:25:59,970
Lang was mature from a young age.

450
00:26:01,250 --> 00:26:04,420
He protected his younger brother

451
00:26:05,450 --> 00:26:06,770
and me.

452
00:26:07,900 --> 00:26:08,380
Qi Zhen,

453
00:26:09,810 --> 00:26:11,670
you abandoned Qi Yan, didn't you?

454
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:17,690
Why?

455
00:26:23,080 --> 00:26:23,560
I...

456
00:26:24,380 --> 00:26:25,340
I had no choice.

457
00:26:29,050 --> 00:26:31,210
I also wanted to raise him properly.

458
00:26:34,010 --> 00:26:35,180
I once thought

459
00:26:35,720 --> 00:26:37,470
that keeping a child by my side was

460
00:26:37,470 --> 00:26:39,600
a blessing among all the misfortunes.

461
00:26:40,820 --> 00:26:42,250
But I only found out later

462
00:26:43,900 --> 00:26:46,830
that it was just the beginning
of another nightmare.

463
00:26:48,860 --> 00:26:50,100
The older Yan grew,

464
00:26:50,700 --> 00:26:53,100
the more he showed
Wen Hongsheng's traits.

465
00:26:53,660 --> 00:26:54,790
He was cold-blooded

466
00:26:55,530 --> 00:26:56,290
and cruel,

467
00:26:57,700 --> 00:26:59,260
and he dared to do anything.

468
00:27:01,190 --> 00:27:02,920
I couldn't teach him properly.

469
00:27:03,820 --> 00:27:05,100
After he entered puberty,

470
00:27:05,100 --> 00:27:07,100
everything just scared me to death.

471
00:27:08,140 --> 00:27:08,860
I knew

472
00:27:10,380 --> 00:27:12,580
he'd only do evil as long as he was alive.

473
00:27:12,660 --> 00:27:13,620
I once wanted

474
00:27:13,620 --> 00:27:15,380
to have him die with me.

475
00:27:16,770 --> 00:27:17,380
But...

476
00:27:18,770 --> 00:27:20,620
But I couldn't do it.

477
00:27:24,580 --> 00:27:26,990
I'm his mother, after all.

478
00:27:34,940 --> 00:27:37,600
Your elder brother's called
Zhou Chuan, right?

479
00:27:38,900 --> 00:27:40,250
He was a good man,

480
00:27:41,620 --> 00:27:42,180
right?

481
00:27:44,580 --> 00:27:46,180
I also have an elder brother,

482
00:27:47,530 --> 00:27:48,490
just like you.

483
00:27:49,820 --> 00:27:51,050
When we reunited,

484
00:27:52,660 --> 00:27:54,210
I was a wanted murderer,

485
00:27:55,490 --> 00:27:57,250
and he was a gentle

486
00:27:57,660 --> 00:27:58,820
family heir.

487
00:28:00,250 --> 00:28:02,180
My brother treated me really well.

488
00:28:02,380 --> 00:28:03,770
Even though we were worlds apart,

489
00:28:03,770 --> 00:28:05,420
in just one week,

490
00:28:05,620 --> 00:28:07,880
he found someone to take the blame for me,

491
00:28:09,050 --> 00:28:11,250
helped me escape the police's pursuit,

492
00:28:11,860 --> 00:28:13,720
and brought me back to the family.

493
00:28:13,940 --> 00:28:14,800
You don't know.

494
00:28:15,940 --> 00:28:16,730
When Wen Lang

495
00:28:17,900 --> 00:28:18,620
took me

496
00:28:20,380 --> 00:28:22,180
to see my biological father,

497
00:28:24,730 --> 00:28:26,100
my father was so happy,

498
00:28:28,730 --> 00:28:29,580
overjoyed,

499
00:28:30,900 --> 00:28:31,900
and so surprised.

500
00:28:32,620 --> 00:28:33,750
His name is Wen Lang?

501
00:28:36,100 --> 00:28:36,660
Yes.

502
00:28:37,210 --> 00:28:38,340
His name is Wen Lang.

503
00:28:42,720 --> 00:28:44,250
I feel really sorry for him.

504
00:28:44,970 --> 00:28:45,830
Compared to me,

505
00:28:46,420 --> 00:28:48,350
he was the one who deserved to live.

506
00:28:50,580 --> 00:28:51,770
Sometimes, family is

507
00:28:51,770 --> 00:28:53,630
such a contradictory existence.

508
00:28:54,620 --> 00:28:55,970
I once loved him,

509
00:28:57,340 --> 00:28:59,210
but because he made a wrong decision,

510
00:28:59,210 --> 00:29:00,740
I hate him more than anyone.

511
00:29:01,660 --> 00:29:03,190
I hate him for abandoning me

512
00:29:04,100 --> 00:29:05,490
and owning everything,

513
00:29:06,210 --> 00:29:07,490
while leaving me

514
00:29:08,100 --> 00:29:10,540
like a battered stray dog,

515
00:29:10,570 --> 00:29:11,700
rotting there,

516
00:29:12,340 --> 00:29:13,820
rotting in the gutter

517
00:29:14,010 --> 00:29:15,180
for a lifetime.

518
00:29:17,100 --> 00:29:18,690
Yet he's up there on the moral high ground

519
00:29:18,690 --> 00:29:20,100
of love and sacrifice,

520
00:29:20,880 --> 00:29:22,880
receiving everyone's respect,

521
00:29:23,660 --> 00:29:24,530
thoughts,

522
00:29:24,810 --> 00:29:25,840
remembrance,

523
00:29:26,530 --> 00:29:27,490
and love.

524
00:29:29,940 --> 00:29:32,860
He gave me what was rightfully mine,
like he was

525
00:29:33,180 --> 00:29:34,660
doing me a favor!

526
00:29:35,900 --> 00:29:36,820
Why?

527
00:29:37,940 --> 00:29:39,620
Why should I accept it?

528
00:29:41,180 --> 00:29:41,940
Why?

529
00:29:46,820 --> 00:29:47,730
We're twins.

530
00:29:49,900 --> 00:29:50,690
Why?

531
00:29:55,920 --> 00:30:03,020
[2012]

532
00:29:56,940 --> 00:29:57,380
Lang.

533
00:29:59,850 --> 00:30:01,370
I think I'm screwed.

534
00:30:03,130 --> 00:30:03,990
I have a feeling

535
00:30:04,700 --> 00:30:05,500
that soon,

536
00:30:05,530 --> 00:30:06,940
the police will find me

537
00:30:07,420 --> 00:30:08,530
and arrest me.

538
00:30:10,380 --> 00:30:10,770
Lang.

539
00:30:14,180 --> 00:30:15,110
I'm a bit scared.

540
00:30:18,340 --> 00:30:19,400
I'm really scared.

541
00:30:20,520 --> 00:30:22,580
Why did you mess with Jiang Hansheng?

542
00:30:24,090 --> 00:30:25,970
Because this guy is really bad.

543
00:30:27,530 --> 00:30:28,530
He's very bad!

544
00:30:29,620 --> 00:30:31,010
This bastard is

545
00:30:31,490 --> 00:30:32,690
like a bug,

546
00:30:32,710 --> 00:30:34,040
crawling into my brain.

547
00:30:34,340 --> 00:30:36,530
He knows everything I'm thinking!

548
00:30:36,970 --> 00:30:37,970
You know what?

549
00:30:38,380 --> 00:30:39,530
He lured me first,

550
00:30:40,140 --> 00:30:41,970
and then provoked me!

551
00:30:42,140 --> 00:30:44,050
He's using me, Lang!

552
00:30:46,140 --> 00:30:47,490
What should I do?

553
00:30:53,530 --> 00:30:55,490
How can I escape?

554
00:30:55,800 --> 00:30:56,630
Wen Lang,

555
00:30:57,170 --> 00:30:58,650
I'm so scared.

556
00:31:06,670 --> 00:31:08,130
I'll take the fall for you.

557
00:31:10,290 --> 00:31:11,020
It will work.

558
00:31:19,050 --> 00:31:20,180
I'm squeaky-clean.

559
00:31:21,010 --> 00:31:22,470
They won't find anything.

560
00:31:23,940 --> 00:31:25,070
I'll tell the police

561
00:31:25,940 --> 00:31:27,200
that you kidnapped me.

562
00:31:29,210 --> 00:31:30,820
On August 17th
and the couple of days following,

563
00:31:30,820 --> 00:31:32,370
I had solid alibis.

564
00:31:33,620 --> 00:31:35,750
I'll let the police take me away first,

565
00:31:35,940 --> 00:31:37,540
and I won't say a word to them.

566
00:31:38,100 --> 00:31:39,380
I'll buy you more time

567
00:31:39,380 --> 00:31:40,100
to escape.

568
00:31:42,730 --> 00:31:43,460
It will work.

569
00:31:45,100 --> 00:31:45,760
But, Qi Yan,

570
00:31:47,340 --> 00:31:48,400
listen carefully.

571
00:31:49,210 --> 00:31:50,610
I'll get you some fake IDs

572
00:31:51,900 --> 00:31:53,760
and have someone send you abroad.

573
00:31:55,900 --> 00:31:57,160
Remember this lesson.

574
00:31:58,580 --> 00:32:00,580
This is the last time I will help you.

575
00:32:01,490 --> 00:32:02,690
Don't ever come back.

576
00:32:05,100 --> 00:32:06,030
Thank you, Lang.

577
00:32:06,770 --> 00:32:07,650
Thank you.

578
00:32:13,970 --> 00:32:15,430
My brother was very smart,

579
00:32:17,320 --> 00:32:19,320
but sometimes he was pretty stupid.

580
00:32:20,530 --> 00:32:22,250
He gave me everything,

581
00:32:23,100 --> 00:32:25,210
standing in front of Jiang Hansheng
and volunteering to take the blame for me.

582
00:32:25,210 --> 00:32:27,470
It was his own choice. I didn't force him.

583
00:32:27,520 --> 00:32:29,380
I didn't force him to do anything.

584
00:32:30,010 --> 00:32:31,870
I accepted everything he gave me.

585
00:32:32,490 --> 00:32:33,940
I deserved it.

586
00:32:34,860 --> 00:32:35,450
Why

587
00:32:36,670 --> 00:32:37,910
should I feel guilty?

588
00:32:40,260 --> 00:32:40,980
Do you think

589
00:32:42,530 --> 00:32:43,700
I seek revenge

590
00:32:43,720 --> 00:32:45,830
on Jiang Hansheng out of guilt?

591
00:32:48,970 --> 00:32:51,180
Jiang Hansheng ruined my plan,

592
00:32:51,490 --> 00:32:52,490
so he must accept

593
00:32:52,490 --> 00:32:53,620
a little punishment.

594
00:32:53,620 --> 00:32:54,940
This is a game,

595
00:32:55,140 --> 00:32:57,000
and games must be played by rules.

596
00:32:59,010 --> 00:33:00,070
And one more thing.

597
00:33:01,860 --> 00:33:03,920
Jiang Hansheng has someone he loves,

598
00:33:06,540 --> 00:33:08,430
the only person

599
00:33:08,690 --> 00:33:10,220
he'll ever love in his life.

600
00:33:14,420 --> 00:33:16,340
And that person is you,

601
00:33:18,360 --> 00:33:19,160
Officer Zhou.

602
00:33:20,840 --> 00:33:21,840
I don't like it.

603
00:33:27,660 --> 00:33:29,120
You are absolutely right,

604
00:33:29,790 --> 00:33:30,350
Qi Yan.

605
00:33:31,340 --> 00:33:32,320
You really are

606
00:33:33,320 --> 00:33:34,010
a stray dog

607
00:33:34,030 --> 00:33:36,620
rotting in the gutter.

608
00:33:37,450 --> 00:33:38,530
You are sick.

609
00:33:40,580 --> 00:33:41,490
You are flawed.

610
00:33:42,800 --> 00:33:44,260
You are incapable of love.

611
00:33:52,860 --> 00:33:53,660
Officer Zhou,

612
00:33:54,620 --> 00:33:55,380
do you think

613
00:33:56,820 --> 00:33:58,100
you can irritate me

614
00:33:58,100 --> 00:33:59,770
with just a few words?

615
00:34:11,090 --> 00:34:12,000
Officer Zhou,

616
00:34:13,010 --> 00:34:15,130
I have a gift for you.

617
00:34:24,860 --> 00:34:25,780
The household registration was

618
00:34:25,780 --> 00:34:27,440
cancelled in September 2012.

619
00:34:28,610 --> 00:34:30,340
I'll look into his business inheritance,

620
00:34:30,340 --> 00:34:31,870
cemetery, and real estate.

621
00:34:40,420 --> 00:34:40,900
Qi Zhen.

622
00:34:42,380 --> 00:34:43,980
We don't have much time left.

623
00:34:44,130 --> 00:34:45,060
I'll just ask you

624
00:34:45,489 --> 00:34:46,690
a question directly.

625
00:34:50,300 --> 00:34:51,560
Okay, please go ahead.

626
00:34:52,010 --> 00:34:53,820
Have you seen Qi Yan since then?

627
00:34:57,300 --> 00:34:58,300
I saw him once.

628
00:34:58,700 --> 00:34:59,170
Where?

629
00:35:00,010 --> 00:35:00,900
In Huaiguang.

630
00:35:01,970 --> 00:35:03,900
I have no idea how he made it either.

631
00:35:04,530 --> 00:35:06,130
He found Jian Liang's house.

632
00:35:06,700 --> 00:35:08,450
Was it before the serial murder cases

633
00:35:08,450 --> 00:35:09,170
or after?

634
00:35:09,610 --> 00:35:10,220
After.

635
00:35:11,300 --> 00:35:12,300
During that time,

636
00:35:12,740 --> 00:35:14,600
the cases were causing an uproar.

637
00:35:15,340 --> 00:35:16,870
Jian Liang was also tied up.

638
00:35:17,740 --> 00:35:20,270
I was the one who opened the door
when Yan came.

639
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:21,530
He brought me a newspaper

640
00:35:21,530 --> 00:35:23,610
reporting a murder case

641
00:35:24,610 --> 00:35:25,940
and didn't say a word.

642
00:35:28,170 --> 00:35:29,420
I knew he did it.

643
00:35:31,650 --> 00:35:32,690
I probably got

644
00:35:34,090 --> 00:35:35,750
too emotionally overwhelmed

645
00:35:36,220 --> 00:35:37,530
and passed out.

646
00:35:40,050 --> 00:35:41,260
When I woke up,

647
00:35:43,740 --> 00:35:44,870
he was already gone.

648
00:35:45,450 --> 00:35:46,740
On the day you met,

649
00:35:47,340 --> 00:35:48,740
was Chief Jian's uniform

650
00:35:48,780 --> 00:35:50,840
still hanging on the wall by the door?

651
00:35:51,170 --> 00:35:52,630
Yes, it was hanging there.

652
00:35:53,450 --> 00:35:54,490
Why do you ask?

653
00:35:56,940 --> 00:35:58,340
Based on previous cases,

654
00:35:58,900 --> 00:35:59,900
Qi Yan's hatred is

655
00:35:59,900 --> 00:36:01,900
projected onto two kinds of people.

656
00:36:02,130 --> 00:36:03,730
First, women in red dresses.

657
00:36:04,610 --> 00:36:06,070
Second, police officers.

658
00:36:09,940 --> 00:36:11,200
And one last question.

659
00:36:12,820 --> 00:36:13,860
"Nanshan Manor."

660
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:15,650
Do you have any impression

661
00:36:15,650 --> 00:36:16,700
of this place?

662
00:36:26,700 --> 00:36:28,050
Nanshan Manor?

663
00:36:31,050 --> 00:36:31,860
Nanshan...

664
00:36:40,130 --> 00:36:41,730
I don't have any impression.

665
00:36:47,900 --> 00:36:50,460
The great show is starting, Officer Zhou.

666
00:36:50,700 --> 00:36:51,900
I'll return it to you.

667
00:36:52,340 --> 00:36:53,260
Watch closely.

668
00:36:55,070 --> 00:36:56,640
I still remember that day.

669
00:36:58,970 --> 00:36:59,900
I miss it so much.

670
00:37:01,450 --> 00:37:02,570
I'll return it to you.

671
00:37:02,570 --> 00:37:03,940
Yeah, get up and take it.

672
00:37:04,260 --> 00:37:05,610
See that pocket watch?

673
00:37:05,940 --> 00:37:06,600
Here you go.

674
00:37:23,170 --> 00:37:23,820
Mr. Yan,

675
00:37:24,530 --> 00:37:25,260
take it back.

676
00:37:51,380 --> 00:37:51,900
Come on,

677
00:37:52,740 --> 00:37:53,600
Officer Jiang.

678
00:37:54,860 --> 00:37:55,820
Let's talk about

679
00:37:58,050 --> 00:37:58,970
your girl.

680
00:38:01,490 --> 00:38:02,550
I didn't expect it.

681
00:38:03,220 --> 00:38:04,480
I really didn't expect

682
00:38:06,130 --> 00:38:07,970
that the tough Officer Jiang

683
00:38:10,340 --> 00:38:12,130
would be shaken

684
00:38:12,130 --> 00:38:13,490
by a little girl.

685
00:38:15,770 --> 00:38:17,690
You're afraid I'll kill her.

686
00:38:31,340 --> 00:38:32,140
Officer Zhou,

687
00:38:33,490 --> 00:38:34,940
do you still think

688
00:38:36,480 --> 00:38:38,880
Jiang Hansheng was innocent when he shot

689
00:38:41,620 --> 00:38:42,880
and killed my brother?

690
00:38:46,810 --> 00:38:48,470
He said he was going to kill me.

691
00:38:49,780 --> 00:38:51,040
He was going to kill me.

692
00:38:52,940 --> 00:38:54,170
Hang in there.

693
00:38:57,460 --> 00:38:59,780
It hurts just looking at it.

694
00:39:01,610 --> 00:39:02,410
Officer Zhou,

695
00:39:03,090 --> 00:39:04,050
see?

696
00:39:05,740 --> 00:39:07,740
Do you see it clearly, Officer Zhou?

697
00:39:12,220 --> 00:39:13,130
Officer Jiang,

698
00:39:14,530 --> 00:39:15,260
does it hurt?

699
00:39:16,010 --> 00:39:17,610
It hurts so much, doesn't it?

700
00:39:18,300 --> 00:39:19,030
Does it hurt?

701
00:39:21,130 --> 00:39:22,390
You just need to beg me,

702
00:39:22,650 --> 00:39:24,380
beg me to give you an injection.

703
00:39:39,730 --> 00:39:41,300
[Captain Tan]

704
00:39:46,360 --> 00:39:46,990
Chief Tan.

705
00:39:47,020 --> 00:39:48,050
The technicians checked

706
00:39:48,050 --> 00:39:50,010
the security cameras on the ring road

707
00:39:50,010 --> 00:39:51,940
and tracked a black sedan

708
00:39:52,010 --> 00:39:53,370
to the wharf outside the city.

709
00:39:53,370 --> 00:39:55,220
The SWAT team has rushed over there.

710
00:39:55,220 --> 00:39:57,990
While searching the cabins
and containers one by one,

711
00:39:57,990 --> 00:39:59,320
they found that sedan.

712
00:39:59,700 --> 00:40:01,450
The action team is going
to inspect the car now.

713
00:40:01,450 --> 00:40:03,260
I'm calling just to ask you...

714
00:40:04,420 --> 00:40:05,050
Retreat!

715
00:40:05,780 --> 00:40:06,380
What?

716
00:40:06,700 --> 00:40:07,450
It's a trap!

717
00:40:07,860 --> 00:40:08,990
Retreat right away!

718
00:40:09,300 --> 00:40:10,340
Everyone, retreat immediately!

719
00:40:10,340 --> 00:40:11,820
Everyone, retreat immediately!

720
00:40:11,820 --> 00:40:12,420
Retreat!

721
00:40:16,050 --> 00:40:17,450
What's the situation now?

722
00:40:17,450 --> 00:40:18,850
Has everyone pulled out?

723
00:40:18,920 --> 00:40:19,780
Yes, they have.

724
00:40:20,570 --> 00:40:22,740
Qi Yan has
strong anti-detection awareness.

725
00:40:22,740 --> 00:40:23,820
He'll set traps.

726
00:40:24,450 --> 00:40:25,880
From now on, you must be careful

727
00:40:25,880 --> 00:40:26,810
with every move.

728
00:40:27,380 --> 00:40:28,970
Okay, you, too.

729
00:40:38,430 --> 00:40:39,890
We're running out of time.

730
00:41:28,700 --> 00:41:29,260
Speak.

731
00:41:32,670 --> 00:41:33,500
Okay, I got it.

732
00:41:35,300 --> 00:41:36,780
The police suddenly retreated

733
00:41:36,780 --> 00:41:37,910
right before they went in.

734
00:41:37,910 --> 00:41:39,500
Although the car blew up successfully,

735
00:41:39,500 --> 00:41:40,960
none of them were injured.

736
00:41:46,780 --> 00:41:47,710
You may pull out.

737
00:41:55,040 --> 00:41:56,770
They already took my bait

738
00:41:58,090 --> 00:42:00,490
but slipped off the hook
at the last minute.

739
00:42:03,620 --> 00:42:05,350
This must not be a coincidence.

740
00:42:06,900 --> 00:42:07,430
It was...

741
00:42:09,110 --> 00:42:10,370
It was Jiang Hansheng?

742
00:42:15,380 --> 00:42:16,090
Smart.

743
00:42:22,570 --> 00:42:24,530
Here are all the properties
under Wen Hongsheng's name.

744
00:42:24,530 --> 00:42:26,570
He used to be the boss
of Dongsheng Company,

745
00:42:26,570 --> 00:42:28,090
owning 14 properties under his name,

746
00:42:28,090 --> 00:42:30,020
as well as 3 company headquarters.

747
00:42:33,220 --> 00:42:34,550
They don't seem like it.

748
00:42:35,570 --> 00:42:36,090
No.

749
00:42:36,700 --> 00:42:37,570
Nanshan Manor can't be

750
00:42:37,570 --> 00:42:38,970
an ordinary place.

751
00:42:39,780 --> 00:42:40,530
It must mean

752
00:42:41,420 --> 00:42:42,880
something special to him.

753
00:42:44,490 --> 00:42:46,090
Check under Wen Lang's name.

754
00:42:46,190 --> 00:42:46,790
Okay.

755
00:43:05,700 --> 00:43:06,300
Qi Yan.
